You are here: SALESFORCE HELP DOCS ANALYTICS Access Insights from the Analytics Mobile App

Analytics on mobile gives you a fast, fluid way to discover the compelling insights within your data and to share the right visuals wherever you are. This page has resources for Analytics in the Salesforce app and Analytics for iOS and Android.

NOTE The Analytics Mobile App isn’t available on the App Store in mainland China.
CRM Analytics gives you multiple ways to get insights on the go: CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app and CRM Analytics for iOS and Android. Find out which mobile experience is right for you.
CRM Analytics Mobile Features
Click the link to download CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app, or CRM Analytics for iOS and Android.
CRM Analytics in the Salesforce mobile app gives you several ways to access and interact with dashboards.
Access your data anywhere with the CRM Analytics for iOS and Android mobile apps.
